profile:
We specialize in the design and construction of pre-engineered and conventional steel buildings for commercial, industrial and agricultural requirements. We will work with you to design your custom build upon request, whether you choose steel, wood or concrete block.

With competitive pricing, eco-friendly and environmentally-friendly options, coupled with experienced staff, Southwest & Midwest Design & Construction Ltd. is a great way to have an efficient, cost-effective building made just the way you like.

We've put our name on a variety of projects, from water-treatment plants to airplane hangars, micro-breweries and emergency rooms, from sunny southern Alberta to the tundra of the Northwest Territories.

Our projects dot the agricultural landscape. We've worked with Vitera, Bayer, Monsanto, DuPont, Cargill, Pioneer, UFA, Case, Western Tractor (John Deere) and Richardson.

Our commercial projects bear names such as Rona, Shell Canada, Peavey Mart, Volkswagen, BFI, McCain, Home Hardware, Finning, Princess Auto, Tim Hortons and more.
